ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="30fd829f-653c-455e-b323-506d6b3b6243" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Graph Daily DMI w/ WeighBack" Description="Graph showing daily Dry Matter Intake with Weighbacks" CreatedDT="2013-08-21T14:21:02.93" ModifiedDT="2014-05-19T16:24:29.653" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAKl0=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select ReportDate, PenNumber , PenName, sum(AF) as TotalAF, avg(DMPct) as AvgDMPct, avg(case when PenCount = 0 then 0 else AF / PenCount end) as AvgAFHd, case when sum(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(AF) / sum(PenCount) end as WAvgAFHd, sum(AF * DMPct) as TotalDM, avg(case when PenCount = 0 then 0 else DMPct * AF / PenCount end) as AvgDMHd, case when Avg(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(DMPct * AF) / Avg(PenCount) end as WAvgDMHd, sum(case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalWBAF, sum(case when AF >= 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalDropAF , sum(DMPct * case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalWBDM, sum(case when AF >= 0 then DMPct * AF else 0 end) as TotalDropDM , avg(case when PenCount = 0 then 0 else case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end / PenCount end) as AvgWBAFHd , case when sum(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end) / sum(PenCount) end as WAvgWBAFHd , avg(case when PenCount = 0 then 0 else case when AF < 0 then DMPct * AF else 0 end / PenCount end) as AvgWBDMHd , case when sum(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(case when AF < 0 then DMPct * AF else 0 end) / sum(PenCount) end as WAvgWBDMHd , case when sum(case when AF >= 0 then AF else 0 end) = 0 then 0 else sum(case when AF < 0 then -AF else 0 end) / sum(case when AF >= 0 then AF else 0 end)*100 end as PctOfWB , avg(PenCount) as AvgPenCount
from ( select case when p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID then 1 else -1 end * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) as AF, convert(date, it.TransactionDT) as ReportDate, l.LocationName as PenName, p.PenNumber as PenNumber, it.DMPct, l.LocationName, case when p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID then 0 else 1 end as IsWeighback, (select top 1 [Count] from PenCountChange where PenGID = p.PenGID and InventoryItemType = 3 and CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT order by CreatedDT desc) as PenCount from InventoryTransaction it join Ingredient i on i.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID or p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = p.LocationGID join Company c on c.CompanyGID = l.CompanyGID ) p group by ReportDate, PenName, PenNumber</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
